# Normalize all text files to LF checkouts on every platform.
# Windows Git defaults to core.autocrlf=true, which rewrites LF blobs to
# CRLF on checkout. README.md is embedded verbatim via include_str! into
# the mdtree-project snapshot fixture and compared against the LF content
# baked into the committed example .mdtree databases, so a CRLF checkout
# on windows-latest breaks that equality check. Forcing eol=lf keeps every
# platform's checkout byte-identical to the LF blobs stored in git.
* text=auto eol=lf
